  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下国家代码体系的演变关系。目前内部系统里混用了好几种标准，FIPS、GEC、GENC这些，大家经常搞混。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "GENC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，您是想画一个对比图？我注意到FIPS和GEC都是美国主导的，GENC算是它们的替代方案吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "GENC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，FIPS 10-4是联邦信息处理标准，GEC是地理政治实体代码，后来NGA推出了GENC作为现代化替代。另外IRS的MeF系统还在用GEC做税务申报。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "GENC",
        "IRS MeF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把美国相关的代码放在一个子图里：FIPS 10-4、GEC、GENC，还有IRS MeF。FIPS到GEC的转换规则是去掉前三位、加四位？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🇺🇸 US codes",
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "GENC",
        "IRS MeF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "差不多，FIPS转GEC是-3+4，GEC转IRS MeF是-13+1。这些转换规则要标在连线上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "IRS MeF"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加转换标注。那国际方面呢？ISO 3166应该是核心吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🌐 Int'l codes",
        "ISO 3166"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，ISO 3166是国际主流，但北约有自己的两套代码——老的那套和新的。老的跟FIPS有对应关系，新的已经跟ISO对齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ISO 3166",
        "🧭 old NATO",
        "FIPS 10-4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我把北约旧代码和ISO 3166放在国际子图里。FIPS和老北约之间标个±表示大致对应，ISO和GENC之间也标±？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🌐 Int'l codes",
        "🧭 old NATO",
        "ISO 3166",
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GENC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，±表示不完全一对一的映射关系。对了，每个节点都要加超链接，指向对应的官方文档或维基页面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "GENC",
        "IRS MeF",
        "ISO 3166",
        "🧭 old NATO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "FIPS指向维基百科的FIPS 10-4页面，GEC指向NGA的GEC注册表，IRS MeF指向irs.gov的countrycodes页面。GENC也是NGA的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "IRS MeF",
        "GENC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "GENC的链接用genc/根目录就行，不用具体到register。ISO 3166的链接我想用解码表那个锚点，因为还涉及ccTLD、ISO 639语言代码、ISO 4217货币代码的关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GENC",
        "ISO 3166"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整。ISO 3166现在指向Decoding_table锚点，备注里注明了new NATO、ccTLD、ISO 639、ISO 4217的关联。老北约的链接用List of NATO country codes？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ISO 3166",
        "🧭 old NATO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。整体结构看起来清晰多了——左边是美国代码体系，右边是国际体系，中间用虚线表示映射关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "🇺🇸 US codes",
        "🌐 Int'l codes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：GENC在US codes子图里，但它和ISO 3166有±映射，这个设计没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GENC",
        "🇺🇸 US codes",
        "ISO 3166"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，GENC虽然是美国NGA维护的，但设计上就是要跟国际标准对齐，所以放在US子图、连到ISO是合理的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GENC",
        "🇺🇸 US codes",
        "ISO 3166"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。所有六个节点都加了点击跳转，转换规则标注在连线上，两个子图区分了美国体系和国际体系。标题用\"Country Codes\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Country Codes",
        "FIPS 10-4",
        "GEC",
        "GENC",
        "IRS MeF",
        "ISO 3166",
        "🧭 old NATO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这个图够用了。下次开会就用这个给大家讲清楚为什么我们的系统要逐步从GEC迁移到GENC，同时保持跟ISO的兼容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GEC",
        "GENC",
        "ISO 3166"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
